2. `x1 = replace(I, lc, ZERO)`      # erase the singleton cell  
3. `shape = leastcolor(x1)`        # now the shape color is the only non‑zero color  
4. `x2 = replace(x1, shape, lc)`    # recolor the shape with the singleton color  
5. `O = x2`                  # final output grid.
